{"tid":969770,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《大黃蜂》大陸開畫首日即破億人民幣","createTime":"2019-01-05T10:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T01:42:02.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b697c9a6c95ebdc137276ad43236221511c26fe4","tid":969770,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:00:14.000Z","msg":"荷李活電影《大黃蜂》（Bumblebee）上月起已在各地開畫，今次由查費斯奈捷（Travis Knight）負責執導，被讚係《變形金剛》（Transformers）電影系列中評價最好作品，截至前日嘅全球累積票房為1.92億美元（近15億港元），呢套戲嘅拍攝成本為1.35億美元（逾10億港元）。<br />\n《大黃蜂》口碑不俗，昨日終於在中國正式上映，開畫首日已破億票房，踏入第二天暫時累積1.7億人民幣，成為全中國票房冠軍，但比唔上第五集《變形金剛：終極戰士》（Transformers：The Last Knight）首日破3億人民幣嘅紀錄。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190105/59107729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F59107729&d=DkgZhRgRkBwa%2FGq7%2B9i4CgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=958afa70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F59107729&h=00bd827c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190105/59107729</a>"},{"pid":"6169ebdb7902dc4b026c2b4120e83e4b76512d40","tid":969770,"uid":212399,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"咁仲洗唔洗翻去繼承家業<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acb37b26851e33f0aa40f5626bd33c002b8c7e5","tid":969770,"uid":55493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"應該唔洗返去做nike啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2c12af337eb92212e419b2e4d31a435489b62e","tid":969770,"uid":44823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"贏就贏粒糖<br />\n輸就贏間廠"},{"pid":"31143feb8b7ed8ee234631f8e8beeb648b2ada50","tid":969770,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite